===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Maxie (Masters)}}
Maxie, in his {{pkmn|Omega Ruby and Alpha Sapphire}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Groudon}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Maxie became a playable sync pair on May 31, 2021.

Maxie has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].

